[4mOVERVIEW[0m
Filter out indels that exceed the specified size

[4mPROPERTIES[0m
  [1msize[0m   Number
    The maximum size of an INDEL to pass

[4mAVAILABLE FIELDS[0m
  [1mfilter_status[0m
    The size of an indel is less than or equal to size

[4mFILTER DESCRIPTION[0m
The size of an indel is less than or equal to size

